import React from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import { motion } from 'framer-motion'; import Card from '../../components/Card'; import Button from '../../components/Button'; const FundManagerDashboardPage: React.FC = () => { // Mock data const fundManagerInfo = { name: 'Sarah Johnson', role: 'Senior Fund Manager', totalFundsManaged: 2500000.00 }; const pendingRequests = [ { id: 1, hospitalName: 'City General Hospital', amount: 5000.00, reason: 'Emergency equipment purchase', urgency: 'High', requestDate: '2024-01-15', hospitalId: 'HOSP001' }, { id: 2, hospitalName: 'Regional Medical Center', amount: 8000.00, reason: 'Facility maintenance', urgency: 'Medium', requestDate: '2024-01-14', hospitalId: 'HOSP002' }, { id: 3, hospitalName: 'Community Health Clinic', amount: 3000.00, reason: 'Staff training program', urgency: 'Low', requestDate: '2024-01-13', hospitalId: 'HOSP003' } ]; const quickActions = [ { title: 'Review Requests', description: 'Approve or reject pending fund requests', icon: 'ðŸ“‹', path: '/fund-manager/approve-reject', color: 'from-blue-500 to-blue-600' }, { title: 'Transfer History', description: 'View all approved and rejected transfers', icon: 'ðŸ“Š', path: '/fund-manager/transfer-history', color: 'from-green-500 to-green-600' }, { title: 'Analytics', description: 'View funding trends and statistics', icon: 'ðŸ“ˆ', path: '#', color: 'from-purple-500 to-purple-600' } ]; const getUrgencyColor = (urgency: string) => { switch (urgency.toLowerCase()) { case 'high': return 'bg-red-100 text-red-800'; case 'medium': return 'bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800'; case 'low': return 'bg-green-100 text-green-800'; default: return 'bg-gray-100 text-gray-800'; } }; return (
{/* Header */}

Welcome back, {fundManagerInfo.name}!

Role: {fundManagerInfo.role}

 {/* Summary Cards */}

Total Funds Managed

${fundManagerInfo.totalFundsManaged.toLocaleString()}

Pending Requests

{pendingRequests.length}

Awaiting review

This Month

$125,000

Funds approved
{/* Quick Actions */}

Quick Actions

{quickActions.map((action) => (
{action.icon}

{action.title}

{action.description}

 ))}
{/* Pending Fund Requests */}

Pending Fund Requests

{pendingRequests.length > 0 ? (
{pendingRequests.map((request) => (

{request.hospitalName}

{request.urgency}
Amount: ${request.amount.toLocaleString()} Date: {request.requestDate} ID: {request.hospitalId}

{request.reason}

Request #{request.id}

))}
) : (

No Pending Requests

All fund requests have been reviewed and processed.

)}
); }; export default FundManagerDashboardPage;
